# Arrow API
An API to sync WooCommerce with Smartequip and GlobalShop.

## Arrow with Smartequip APIs list
## API that sent orders from smartequip to Arrow [/seorders]
### Purchase Order Details  [POST]

+ Request (application/json)

        {
            "seorderid": "1234",
            "billing": [
                    {
                        "first_name": "John",
                        "last_name": "Doe",
                        "address_1": "969 Market",
                        "address_2": "",
                        "city": "San Francisco",
                        "state": "CA",
                        "postcode": "94103",
                        "country": "US",
                        "email": "john.doe@example.com",
                        "phone": "(555) 555-5555"
                    }
            ],
            "shipping": [
                    {
                        "first_name": "John",
                        "last_name": "Doe",
                        "address_1": "969 Market",
                        "address_2": "",
                        "city": "San Francisco",
                        "state": "CA",
                        "postcode": "94103",
                        "country": "US",
                        "email": "john.doe@example.com",
                        "phone": "(555) 555-5555"
                    }
            ],
            "line_items": [
                    {
                        "product_id": 93,
                        "quantity": 3
                    },
                    {
                        "product_id": 22,
                        "variation_id": 23,
                        "quantity": 2
                    }
            ],
            "shipping_lines": [
                    {
                        "method_id": "flat_rate",
                        "method_title": "Flat Rate",
                        "total": 10
                    }
            ],
            "customerid": "5673",
            "locationid": "87453",
        }

+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Headers

            UUID: 123456789009876543211234567890123456
            Accountnumber: 123432343
            Username: seaccount
            Password: sepassword
            Locationid: 1243
            Language: ISO 639-1

    + Body

            {
                "status": "success",
                "seorderid": "1234",
                "arroworderid": "4321"
            }


## API to sent SO Number from Arrow to Smartequip [/sesonumber]
### SO Number from Arrow to Smartequip [GET]

+ Request (application/json)

        {
            "seorderid": "1234"
        }

+ Response 201 (application/json)

    + Headers

            UUID: 123456789009876543211234567890123456
            Accountnumber: 123432343
            Username: seaccount
            Password: sepassword
            Locationid: 1243
            Language: ISO 639-1

    + Body

            {
                "status": "success",
                "seorderid": "1234",
                "SOnumber": "09876"
            }

