## API that sent SO Number from Globalshop to Arrow [/gssonumber]
### SO Number to receive from Globalshop to Arrow [POST]

+ Request (application/json)

        {
            "wooseorderid" : 1234-4536,
        }

+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Body

            {
                "status": "success",
                "WooSOnumber": "435657",
                "GSSOnumber": "09876"
            }
            

